_sText:
+ This is the Second Capture The Flag release useing TopHattWaffle's ctf prefab. 

+ It took me around 30 mins to make. 

+ I made it immediatly after seeing TopHattWaffles ctf prefab 
http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/5511

+ This map will work on prety much any type of server

+ First to 5 caps wins

+ Drop primary weapon to pick up the flag.

+ Speed boost if you cap.

+ Cap in the "Cap" area.

+ Run over the droped flag to return it.

+ I hope to see more releases using this prefab.

+ Good luck and Have Fun.
